OL,3,C'We don't want your support': Bristol
OL,4,CRovers condemns racist abuse of player
OL,6,FBristol Rovers Football Club has said
OL,7,Fit "will not tolerate" racist abuse
OL,8,Fafter one of its players was targeted
OL,9,Ffollowing a match this weekend.
OL,11,FForward Shaq Forde received racist
OL,12,Fabuse online following the Rovers'
OL,13,FLeague One game at Reading on Saturday
OL,14,F26 October.
OL,16,FThe club said that shortly after the
OL,17,Fmatch ended, a message containing
OL,18,F"abusive and racist" language was sent
OL,19,Fto the 20-year-old a message from an
OL,20,FInstagram account.
