OL,3,C'We don't want your support': Bristol
OL,4,CRovers condemns racist abuse of player
OL,6,FMatt Taylor's side has now said this
OL,7,Fis the second incident of racial abuse
OL,8,Fin less than two weeks and that it
OL,9,Fcondemns it in the strongest terms.
OL,11,FIt added the message is now being
OL,12,Finvestigated and the club will work
OL,13,Fwith the police and Meta, Instagram's
OL,14,Fparent company, to do so.
OL,16,FIn a statement, it said: "Bristol
OL,17,FRovers is infuriated by racist abuse
OL,18,Fdirected at Shaq Forde in the
OL,19,Faftermath of Saturday's Sky Bet League
OL,20,FOne match at Reading.
