OL,3,C'We don't want your support': Bristol
OL,4,CRovers condemns racist abuse of player
OL,6,F"We will always, unequivocally, stand
OL,7,Fside-by-side with any victim of
OL,8,Fdiscriminatory abuse. The Club is
OL,9,Fcommitted to educating on the damage
OL,10,Fthat any form of abuse has.
OL,12,F"Shaq is not the only Bristol Rovers
OL,13,Fplayer to receive racial abuse, with
OL,14,Fan incident under investigation only
OL,15,Flast week. Even more sickening is that
OL,16,Fsome of these messages come from
OL,17,Findividuals claiming to be Bristol
OL,18,FRovers supporters.
