OL,6,FThe club statement added: "Enough is
OL,7,Fenough."
OL,9,F"We are sick and tired of racist
OL,10,Fbehaviour blighting sport. Our players
OL,11,Fare sick and tired of vile racist
OL,12,Fabuse that is thoughtlessly shared in
OL,13,Fresponse to performances in their job.
OL,14,FOur supporters - our real supporters -
OL,15,Fare sick and tired of being in any way
OL,16,Fassociated with those 'fans' who
OL,17,Fcomfortably send such abhorrent
OL,18,Fmessages.
OL,20,F"We will not tolerate it.
