OL,3,C'We don't want your support': Bristol
OL,4,CRovers condemns racist abuse of player
OL,6,F"To the person who sent Shaq this
OL,7,Fracist message, and to any person who
OL,8,Fclaims to be a Gashead and engages in
OL,9,Fsimilarly deplorable behaviour, we
OL,10,Fsimply say this: You are not a Bristol
OL,11,FRovers fan. You are not welcome at The
OL,12,FMemorial Stadium. We do not want your
OL,13,Fsupport.
OL,15,F"Discrimination in any form will not
OL,16,Fbe accepted at Bristol Rovers and we
OL,17,Furge all supporters to join us in
OL,18,Funison with this message."
