OL,3,C'We don't want your support': Bristol
OL,4,CRovers condemns racist abuse of player
OL,6,FHosts Reading also said the club
OL,7,F"strongly condemns the racist abuse
OL,8,Fsent to Bristol Rovers player Shaq
OL,9,FForde".
OL,11,FIn a statement, The Royals added: "We
OL,12,Fwill work alongside Saturday's
OL,13,Fvisitors to ensure the perpetrator is
OL,14,Fidentified and evidence is provided to
OL,15,Fthe relevant authorities.
OL,17,F"Reading Football Club would like to
OL,18,Fpass our support onto Shaq. No
OL,19,Findividual, whether on or off the
OL,20,Fpitch, should be subjected to such
OL,21,Fabuse. We stand by you Shaq."
